ref=\"https://lih.kg/2380593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2380593</a><br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">只要有大批香港人離開，會造成現時已經虛弱既經濟徹底崩潰，而中共強行鎖國則引來百國聯軍。</span> 所以，不論你係撐 Trump 既手足、定係支持滅共既手足，今次 BNO Visa 係時候身體力行，用你對腳投票去支持 Trump 呢條滅共戰線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多你一個好多，少你一個唔掂！你既決定將會成為世界走向正義定係腐敗既關鍵因素！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8470cc62a8f329a8805813796f37ead4f87c42a2","tid":2380931,"uid":227588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e941ac0ce73aa4b665f6c0a37011698c8cd9a786","tid":2380931,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T09:07:19.000Z","msg":"美國要忍耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T17:50:32.000Z","msg":"DKLM，一大強國喎，執柒咗去算吧啦！"},{"pid":"2e28101e053ac3e87092757f309902f07a6e9934","tid":2380931,"uid":92188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T17:52:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L8rXP192gHc&amp;t=3s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DL8rXP192gHc%26t%3D3s&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BJnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=31e2e9c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L8rXP192gHc&amp;t=3s</a><br />\n台灣2022年之前應該玩完"},{"pid":"5f6f4849181d248ed1c47faad60f0b67a8060ce1","tid":2380931,"uid":258328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T17:52:43.000Z","msg":"屌你老母中共，依家唔打幾時打，時機過咗就無<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5358417c69dbb3787ff8be9ebe63a9b3c99210a6","tid":2380931,"uid":76398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T17:58:45.000Z","msg":"睇多陣先，之前支那D演習話就話南海但都係近岸"},{"pid":"8ffa66686d78319708db5ce2352d0446dac39972","tid":2380931,"uid":3297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7ec24f7a5b8910659dc22361675a895149aaba4","tid":2380931,